'''斯蒂芬·戴维·達爾德里'''（'''Stephen Daldry'''，{{bd|1961年|5月2日||}}），[[大英帝國勳章|CBE]]，[[英国|英國]][[舞台劇|舞台劇]]及電影[[导演|導演]]，亦是[[電影監製|電影監製]]。至今執導的電影長片，包括《[[跳出我天地|舞動人生]]》、《[[时时刻刻|時時刻刻]]》、《[[讀愛|為愛朗讀]]》、《[[心靈鑰匙|心靈鑰匙]]》都獲得高度評價，並提名為[[奧斯卡最佳導演獎|奧斯卡最佳導演獎]]。舞台劇方面，則屢次贏得[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]最佳導演獎。

==生平==
===早年===
杜德利出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[多塞特郡|多塞特郡]]，父親Patrick Daldry是銀行經理；母親Cherry Thompson是歌手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/92/Stephen-Daldry.html |title=Stephen Daldry Biography (1961?-) |publisher=Filmreference.com |accessdate=2010-01-14 |archive-date=2010-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113130720/http://filmreference.com/film/92/Stephen-Daldry.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在杜德利14歲那年，父親死於癌症<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/2697745.stm |title=Stephen Daldry: Cometh the Hours |accessdate=2010-02-19 |archive-date=2006-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060630115039/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/2697745.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大學在[[谢菲尔德大学|謝菲爾德大学]]就讀，期間是學校劇團SuTCo（謝菲爾德大学劇團／Sheffield University Theatre Company）主席。1985年決定輟學轉到[[克鲁西布剧院|克鲁西布剧院]]當學徒，1988年出師，亦曾於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[東15演技學校|東15演技學校]]（East 15 Acting School）受訓。

===私人生活===
杜德利曾與佈景設計師{{le|Ian MacNeil (scenic designer)|Ian MacNeil (scenic designer)|Ian MacNeil}}有過一段長達13年的關係<ref>{{cite web |author=The Broadway League |url=http://www.ibdb.com/person.php?id=14547 |title=Stephen Daldry |publisher=IBDB |accessdate=2010-01-14 |archive-date=2010-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102203808/http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=14547 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2001年，與女性好友Lucy Sexton結婚，兩人育有一女Annabel Clare（2003年出生）<ref name=Advocate>{{cite news |last=Giltz |first=Michael |title=The golden Hours |work=The Advocate |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1589/is_2003_March_18/ai_99850228 |date=18 March 2003 |accessdate=2008-05-29 |archive-date=2008-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120182627/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1589/is_2003_March_18/ai_99850228 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Stephen Daldry |work=Matt & Andrej Koymasky - The Living Room - Biographies |url=http://andrejkoymasky.com/liv/fam/biod1/dald1.html |accessdate=2008-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509161312/http://andrejkoymasky.com/liv/fam/biod1/dald1.html |archivedate=2008-05-09 }}</ref>。當被問及性傾向時，杜德利則形容自己為同性戀，並表示這樣說只是為了避免引起困惑<ref name=Guardian2009>{{cite news |title=How Britain became the toast of Broadway: Last week Billy Elliot won 10 Tony awards in New York, crowning a glorious year for British theatre at home and abroad. The following morning we caught up with Stephen Daldry, the award-winning musical's director, to talk about this theatrical renaissance, juggling stage and film projects - and his complex love life |last=Wood |first=Gaby |date=14 June 2009 |newspaper=The Observer |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2009/jun/14/stephen-daldry-billy-elliot-tonys |accessdate=2010-02-19 |archive-date=2009-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090730151843/http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2009/jun/14/stephen-daldry-billy-elliot-tonys |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

